*** My new series, This is Not a Conspiracy Theory, is now live: vimeo.com/ondemand/tinact ***
Remixing is a folk art but the techniques are the same ones used at any level of creation: copy, transform, and combine. You could even say that everything is a remix.
If you'd like to support my work, you can do so here: everythingisaremix.info/donate/
